{"tid":1585461,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際文宣] Twitter 戰線係咪要統一？","createTime":"2019-09-21T15:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T15:54:44.000Z","uid":77937,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7477914a17329e45490ccef9edc88516dd5df0","tid":1585461,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"1. 而家hashtag 其實好亂，可唔可以係到討論到共識？<br />\nSuggestion:<br />\n<br />\na) 行動 － 個一個weekend 會有咩protest，有咩行動，assembly等<br />\n例：#929globalmarch<br />\n<br />\nb) 黑警<br />\n例：#HongKongPoliceTerrorist / #PoliceBruality <br />\n<br />\nc) 長期使用，引起討論／比人search<br />\n例：#Chinazi , #HongKong , #HongKongProtests<br />\n<br />\nd）突發<br />\n如果有記者會爆料，到時先再制定。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以係到加覺得有用既hashtag。行動方面，我認為大約每星期update一次好d。<br />\n<br />\n2. &nbsp;推既時間<br />\n以我理解，twitter既trend係根據個段時間幾多人用而上worldwide trend。<br />\n&nbsp;Suggest 2個時段都推：<br />\n<br />\na) 香港時間2200（US West Coast 0700 / US East Coast 1000)<br />\n－ 可以推到d news 比US睇<br />\n<br />\nb) 香港時間1500 (London time: 0800)<br />\n－理由同上，佔據EU朝早時間<br />\n<br />\n內容方面，請主要用英文。相信睇一睇d news 都有大把source。suggest 係推既時間，有關行動同黑警既內容都可以一齊tweet。<br />\n<br />\n每一個tweet hashtag唔應該超過5個，係呢到finalise左之後就可以統一twitter 文宣戰線。歡迎任屌。"},{"pid":"6855c55484f0d4421bfde75b13a5d61b64148201","tid":1585461,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:24:54.000Z","msg":"721 831 San Uk Ling"},{"pid":"393d01f2ea1f8710208f502abbcc58ae60a60838","tid":1585461,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:33:54.000Z","msg":"721 831 San Uk Ling"},{"pid":"33b2eb6cc076e1091f6c64b4dfb239f1a3c0d146","tid":1585461,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:38:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>【All you need to know about Hong Kong Protests 2019】2.0</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585367\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585367</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【國際文宣】<br />\n抗爭英文版懶人包<br />\n請盡量用英文推post<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">share去twitter同reddit</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"17e8f8a8d6c18f9b01ec9419777c514d1c96f661","tid":1585461,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:41:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b0239832c633fdc3728b6592d4e204c2e7e3f128","tid":1585461,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c637dae2871e3e010eced7e7c46cb316bbb4caba","tid":1585461,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:48:36.000Z","msg":"你入twitter tg gp有哂共識<br />\n唔好自己係度開共識po"},{"pid":"e9e4dd6810f0b15c24db62307fc08633478fe096","tid":1585461,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c637dae2871e3e010eced7e7c46cb316bbb4caba","tid":1585461,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:48:36.000Z","msg":"你入twitter tg gp有哂共識<br />\n唔好自己係度開共識po"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:51:37.000Z","msg":"收到，搵搵link先。大家唔好推"},{"pid":"d23b53be1bb6b7b4beb4d3bdf557bcdf50bddc38","tid":1585461,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9e4dd6810f0b15c24db62307fc08633478fe096","tid":1585461,"uid":77937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c637dae2871e3e010eced7e7c46cb316bbb4caba","tid":1585461,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:48:36.000Z","msg":"你入twitter tg gp有哂共識<br />\n唔好自己係度開共識po"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:51:37.000Z","msg":"收到，搵搵link先。大家唔好推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:53:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=e004bb69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a>"},{"pid":"e2cf85d3462c10505a74c2fdc9245f3391edadd7","tid":1585461,"uid":180124,"like":0,"di